4Geeks Academy offers a Full Stack Developer Bootcamp designed to equip students with in-demand skills in JavaScript and Python over an 18-week program. Participants learn web development, algorithm scripting, and app-building with front-end libraries and APIs, culminating in a hands-on project. The program features three classes a week with a favorable teacher-to-student ratio of 1:7 and provides a Full-Stack Developer certificate upon completion. No prior coding experience is required. Instruction is available in English or Spanish based on campus. For more details, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/part-time-full-stack-developer). stop